fields.summary: [Epic] User Authentication and Access
fields.description: This epic covers the functionality related to user authentication and access.

fields.summary: As a user, I want to sign up with my email and password
fields.description: As a user, I want to sign up with my email and password so that I can access the Quidditch app.

fields.summary: Test case for: As a user, I want to sign up with my email and password
fields.description:
Test case:
Given a new user
When they enter valid email and password and click sign up
Then the account is created and they are redirected to the dashboard

fields.summary: As a user, I want to reset my password
fields.description: As a user, I want to reset my password so that I can regain access if I forget it.

fields.summary: Test case for: As a user, I want to reset my password
fields.description:
Test case:
Given a user has forgotten their password
When they request a password reset
Then they receive an email with a reset link
